        <section id="Apache+Composer+Incubation+Status">
            <title>Apache Composer Incubation Status</title>
            <p>
                This page tracks the project status, incubator-wise. For more general
                project status, look at the
                <a href="http://incubator.apache.org/composer">project website</a>
                .
            </p>
            <p><span class="retired">The Composer project retired on 2008-05-13</span></p>
        </section>
        <section id="Description">
            <title>Description</title>
            <p>Apache Composer would have been a merging of PicoContainer and Plexus. This project has been retired from the incubator.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="News">
            <title>News</title>
            <ul>
                <li>2008-05-09 Project cancelled.  PicoContainer and Plexus will not merge or arrive at Apache as a project.</li>
            </ul>
            <ul>
                <li>2007-10-30 Project accepted for incubation in Apache.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
